1. *Odlazim* u grad (I am leaving for the city).
2. Čekam da *odlazim* na putovanje (I'm waiting to leave for the trip).
3. Moji roditelji su mi rekli da *odlazim* (My parents told me to leave).
4. *Odlazi* čovek iz sobe (The man is leaving the room).
5. *Odlazila* je iz kuće (She left the house).
6. On je *odlazio* bez pozdrava (He was leaving without saying goodbye).
7. *Odlazim* kući (I'm leaving home).